<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Eger</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er die Anfrage der Adressaten nicht schriftlich, sondern nur mündlich beantwortet.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_203" id="101v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_203_r1l16">Der Stat ʒu Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_203_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns ettlıch artıkel vnd ſache <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l18">begert vvıe wır ſölıch ſache bey vns halten vnd handeln . daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l19">eẅch das ſchrıftlıch wıſſen laſſen etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l20">Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır des vormals niht getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l21"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd bey vns niht gewönlıch <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt . daʒ wır <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l22">vmb ſölıch ſache . ſchrıftlıch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l23">daʒ Jr das ın gut verſteet . Denn wo wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l25"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_203_r1l24"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_203" id="101v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als ir uns ettlich artikel und sache
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt und begert, wie wir sölich
                        sache bey uns halten und handeln, daz wir ewch das schriftlich wissen lassen
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex>,</expan> daz wir des vormals niht getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und bey uns niht gewönlich
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, daz wir
                            <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> umb sölich sache schriftlich
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>, daz ir das in gut versteet. Denn
                        wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
